[[File:Concussion_grenade_mortar.jpg|thumb|right|250px|A concussion grenade mortar mounted on a Mobile Defense Unit]]
The '''concussion grenade mortar''' was found on [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Mobile Defense Unit]]s. Also, the [[Hutt Cartel/Legends|Hutt Cartel]] would use them as automated turrets on worlds like [[Nal Hutta/Legends|Nal Hutta]]. It would fire a volley of eight grenades at an enemy target until it or its target is destroyed. The grenades had low accuracy but did do damage to enemy units in the surrounding area.

